nl.tno.stormcv.operation

Class HaarCascadeOp

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.tno.stormcv.operation.OpenCVOp<CVParticle>
      • nl.tno.stormcv.operation.HaarCascadeOp
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, IOperation<CVParticle>, ISingleInputOperation<CVParticle>

    public class HaarCascadeOp
extends OpenCVOp<CVParticle>
implements ISingleInputOperation<CVParticle>
    Detects Haar Cascades in frames/images using OpenCV's CascadeClassifier. The name of the objects detected as well as the model must be provided on construction. It is possible to specify the minimum and maximum dimensions of detections as well.
    Author:
    Corne Versloot
    See Also:
    OpenCV Documentation, Serialized Form
